Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 我到底還能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了改變那如狹隘庭園般的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還活不到人生的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗 相擁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在無意識中被刻上的經驗紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當站在懸崖邊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦難抓住了我的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往更加寬廣的領域\N往更深更大的某處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝著無法預測的世界前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And lt's calling me again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T-J反轉，time shift
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.26,0:01:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在D-1後方的強大磁場中探測到k介子！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.47,0:01:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核力被釋放？ 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.68,0:01:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jupiter現象…這種模式和Tokyo Jupiter…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼alpha小隊不上去？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以D-1為中心有超過屏蔽限度的強大EMP放出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:45.77,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}EMP(Electro_Magnetic Pulse)：電磁脈衝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.14,0:01:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！如果繼續接近下去\N恐怕電子控制系統和機體都會損壞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.35,0:01:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.85,0:01:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這簡直…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與D-1接觸了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機師的心率快速下降！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.75,0:02:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FH服的生命維持裝置停止工作！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去，綾人會…！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-1的脈衝調製模式與RahXephon的聲紋同步了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.26,0:02:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…？！綾人君！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌聲…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-1的形態發生收縮性的改變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.64,0:02:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon完全被D-1包裹住了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EMP強度級別E
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通向未知區域的通道正在形成！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數據聯接系統停止工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃！ 綾人！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-1進入未知區域
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與RahXephon的通迅中斷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.55,0:03:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.07,0:03:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！ 對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧！ 浩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦，來！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來朝比奈他們都沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你到底在說些什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來，一起去玩吧，很無聊，對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？ 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？ 在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還在吉祥寺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？ 真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看著辦不就行了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？不行？真的不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣，不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你嘴巴上還沾著醬汁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你弄乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.15,0:07:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不是Tokyo Jupiter的內部嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的腦袋好像有點不對勁…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在究竟是哪一年？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是2028年嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會回來呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想喝吧？咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的咖啡很好哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，這是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夢，對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不應該在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.56,0:08:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這裡和我認識和住過的東京沒有什麼區別
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.65,0:08:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像平時一樣朝比奈和守在一起玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個世界才是夢境啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不是…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.37,0:08:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這咖啡的顏色和香味是真實了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好了啊，別再亂想了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你看見了蝴蝶的夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是蝴蝶看見了你的夢境(莊周夢蝶)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是無關緊要的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你認為自己感知到的事物是真實的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這個世界不就是真實的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是件幸福的事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不會有戰鬥和痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必再忍耐什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是你感受到的，你自己的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！抱…抱歉！…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必忍耐了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像個男人一樣的做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必介意年齡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要壓抑自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你想做的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照你的想法繼續下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有勉強自己！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有忍耐什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是在自欺欺人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過大家都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不管你怎樣掩飾，\N這就是你想要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:10:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能演奏了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.06,0:10:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調律呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一站：石神井公園
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請檢查您所攜帶的物品以免忘記帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汽車開動時請不要更換座位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一站：石神井公園
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.18,0:11:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面是一則關於在自動販賣機上\N買東西的可愛黑猩猩的報道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天…真是難得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然做好了晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別發牢騷了，快吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.07,0:11:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是想發牢騷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在猩猩養殖場內裝了自動販賣機…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久沒有做飯了，可能做的不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道是不是太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據飼養員說以後會嘗試叫\N黑猩猩清理喝完了的空易拉罐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.55,0:12:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不管這些，綾人君…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名綾人君，能聽到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名綾人君，如果聽到了請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請說話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不知道你現在究竟怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把你的FH服設置到C模式，\N以此通知我們你還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則這樣下去，\N你就無法回我們這邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.66,0:12:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名綾人君！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…你…不回來…，\N…事態…會…很嚴重…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的電視信號好像不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.57,0:13:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人！電話！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是綾人嗎？剛才怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼不說一聲就回去了？\N浩子很擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，明天學校見！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…明天學校見！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了，就這樣好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會感到恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會感到痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜歡的就不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧？我就是這樣想的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了！別開玩笑了！別開玩笑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久遠！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了？！久遠！振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.35,0:14:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,olin…不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:14:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久遠！久遠！…久遠！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕已經不行了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經五小時了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FH服有什麼反應嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在活動狀態和拒絕狀態之間轉換
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.74,0:15:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經幾乎完全是拒絕狀態了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠，現在還不能放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他…這樣呼叫他都沒反應…他…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人，說話！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人，回答啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用…完全沒有回音…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續呼叫，繼續讓他聽到我們的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會放棄的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來找我吧，綾人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:16:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，你應該聽媽媽的話，對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是RahXephon的正統奏者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.84,0:16:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此你才出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有當奏者忠實於樂譜時，才能發揮真正的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即興演奏對你來說還太早了，你應該明白吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對RahXephon調律還不夠成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也不能怪你，你的心受了太多的蒙蔽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.07,0:16:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是？綾人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡你可以安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以過平常的生活，做RahXephon的奏者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在我這個生育你的人的身邊，好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:17:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和媽媽做…不是很好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.94,0:17:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人想做的任何事我都可以為綾人做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為你著想…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說謊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確媽媽什麼都願意為我做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想做畫家，媽媽也沒有反對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但當我希望你在我身邊的時候\N真心希望你在我身邊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽卻總不在，不是嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.47,0:17:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人，我可是在為你工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為你著想…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.85,0:17:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不聽我的話呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的兒子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(MU族語)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼做？該到哪裡去？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我吧！是你吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.28,0:18:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.37,0:18:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.95,0:18:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回真實的世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真實的世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎麼樣的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真實的也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真實的也可以…\N因為這裡讓我不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:19:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不真實，像被什麼纏住了，使我焦躁不安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.34,0:19:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也許是我希望的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我討厭這樣的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡並不存在，因為我沒有活著的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在真實的世界裡，說不定有神名君想逃避的事情在等著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你願意面對，而且有面對的心理準備的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.36,0:19:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要靠自己的力量離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.17,0:20:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，美嶼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EMP脈衝調製反轉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認D-1發生物理性損傷！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動力上升，啟動！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認駕駛員的心率！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人還活著！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.78,0:21:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.34,0:21:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了，找到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.97,0:21:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的oiln…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.35,0:23:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢的低語
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.94,0:23:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重疊的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.65,0:23:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那盡頭看到的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.15,0:23:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon 第十二樂章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑卵
